    <stitle>VT 365 Diesel Engine - 2004 Model Year - OIL PAN, UPPER OIL PAN, and OIL PICKUP TUBE - Installation - Oil
        Pickup Tube
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="s26506.3.2" svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>Oil Pickup Tube</title>
        <figure id="f2650607" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd06/D0663.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>New O-ring</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new O-ring on oil pickup tube. Lubricate O-ring with clean engine oil.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f2650608" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd06/D0661.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Oil pickup tube</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Oil pickup tube mounting bolts, M6 X 16 (3)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install oil pickup tube and three mounting bolts. Tighten bolts to the standard torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
